Phone accessories manufacturer Mobile Outfitters has revealed what it claims to be the thinnest impact bumper for iPhone.The Clear-Coat Fusion Bumper&#8217; has been designed to protect against both corner drops and direct screen hits, even in the case of a 20-foot drop.The bumper measures just 1.99 millimeters, allegedly making it 40% thinner than its closest competitor, and features corner cushions and the company&#8217;s TriActive&#8217; technology to absorb and diffuse impact.The bumper is available for the iPhone 6, 6S and 7 models. For more information see www.moutfitters.com-Relaxnews